    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the the efficacy of TA-650 using Clinical activity
      index (CAI) score and other evaluation indicators in pediatric patients with moderate to
      severe ulcerative colitis after TA-650 administration of at a dose of 5 mg/kg at weeks 0, 2,
      and 6, and then every 8 weeks at weeks 14 and 22. The safety and pharmacokinetics are also
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
